<template>
    <v-container>
      <shop-register-form @submit="onSubmit" />
    </v-container>
  </template>
  
  <script>
  import ShopRegisterForm from '@/components/product/ProductRegisterForm.vue';
  import { mapActions } from 'vuex';
  
  export default {
    components: { ShopRegisterForm },
    name: 'ShopRegisterPage',
    methods: {
      ...mapActions(['requestProduct']),
      async onSubmit(payload) {
        await this.requestProduct(payload);
        await this.$router.push({
          name: 'ShopListPage',
        });
      },
    },
  };
  </script>
  
  <style>
  .product-registration-page {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
  }
  form {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
    margin-top: 20px;
  }
  label {
    font-weight: bold;
  }
  input,
  textarea {
    width: 300px;
    padding: 5px;
    border-radius: 5px;
    border: 1px solid #ccc;
  }
  button {
    padding: 10px 20px;
    border-radius: 5px;
    border: none;
    background-color: #333;
    color: #fff;
    cursor: pointer;
  }
  button:hover {
  }
  </style>
